Package: DHSCcolours
Type: Package
Title: DHSC colour palletes and ggplot2 scales
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alex Betts
Maintainer: Alex Betts <alex.betts@dhsc.gov.uk>
Description: This package contains a suite of functions for working with the
    official DHSC colour scheme. It includes functions to call the colour codes
    of individual colours as well as colour and fill scales for both continuous
    and discrete ggplot aesthetics.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
